item.description: I’m a 19yo student at Ecole 2600 and apprentice at Serma Safety & Security. Here you’ll be able to find some write-ups about interesting challenges that I’ve solved during CTFs (mostly reverse-engineering challenges). Feel free to contact me Formally at p2lu@proton.me Also in discord prince2lu Note: some writeups are relatively old and maybe imprecise
